description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 32, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 96, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Box for East, Stringalong for South, and Stringalong for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80323-14774-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [96 Votes, Common]
